2012-12-03 [wwp]	3.9.0cvs40

	* src/summaryview.c
	* src/mainwindow.c
	Avoid any possible confusion: 0 is not a neutral value when passed
	to main_window_get_mask() - use -1 instead, even in those cases we
	don't care.

2012-12-03 [wwp]	3.9.0cvs39

	* src/toolbar.c
