		Fix previous patch (our own tmp dir is inside
		our rc dir)

2010-08-16 [colin]	3.7.6cvs27

	* src/main.c
		Use temp dir to store logs in Windows. Avoids doing
		get_rc_dir() early, which prevents set_rc_dir()
		working correctly.

