2008-11-14 [colin]	3.6.1cvs27

	* src/mainwindow.c
	* src/summaryview.c
	* src/summaryview.h
	* src/gtk/menu.c
	* src/gtk/menu.h
		Share summaryview's context menu actions with
		the equivalent menu items of the main menu;
		this allows to share accelerators and de-
		duplicate code.

