2006-08-27 [colin]	2.4.0cvs96

	* configure.ac
	* src/plugins/Makefile.am
	* src/plugins/bogofilter/.cvsignore
	* src/plugins/bogofilter/Makefile.am
	* src/plugins/bogofilter/bogofilter.c
