		gtk+ 2.10) from being reported again:
		if Sylpheed-Claws has been compiled against
		GTK+ < 2.9.0 and we're running with GTK+ >= 2.9.0, 
		of if Sylpheed-Claws has been compiled against
		GTK+ >= 2.9.0 and we're running with GTK+ < 2.9.0,
		error out.

