2005-02-14 [colin]	1.0.1cvs6

	* src/compose.c
	* src/procmime.c
		Use quoted-printable instead of 7bit or 8bit
		to encode "^From " and avoid mail corruption 
		on the MTA, as specified by RFC 3156. Thanks
		Hoa for the hint.

