	  po/remove-potcdate.sed	** REMOVED **
	  po/remove-potcdate.sin	** REMOVED **
	  po/stamp-po			** REMOVED **
	  Makefile.am
	  autogen.sh
	  configure.ac
		enable building with automake 1.8.x
		add 'autopoint' to autogen.sh and remove all
		auto-generated files, remove ac/ in favour of
		m4/

