2002-06-26 [paul]	0.7.8claws29

	* src/addrgather.c
	  src/selective_download.c
		don't gettextise empty strings.
		reserved by gettext. gettext("") returns 
		the header entry with meta information, 
		not the empty string

	* po/en_GB.po
		updated

